      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly everything just feels so pointless. like i look at the stars or the sheer scale of the universe and it just hits me that nothing we do matters at all. there's no grand plan, no soul, no meaning... just a cold, dark void. it feels like we're just glitching in the dark for no reason.",
